{
  "name": "morning-boot",
  "version": "0.1.0",
  "description": "晨啟動工作流",
  "category": "G",
  "number": 125,
  "pain_point": "開機要打開一堆程式",
  "commercial": "✅",
  "language": "Python",
  "dependencies": [
    "subprocess",
    "click",
    "rich"
  ],
  "agent_compatible": true,
  "mcp_ready": true,
  "intent_triggers": [
    "每天早上開機都要手動打開一堆程式",
    "幫我設定晨間工作流自動啟動環境",
    "上班前的準備工作能不能自動化？",
    "怎麼讓電腦開機就自動設定好工作環境",
    "我想一個指令就開好所有工作需要的 app",
    "每天早上啟動固定程式清單的腳本",
    "自動化開機工作流程，減少準備時間"
  ],
  "examples": [
    {
      "query": "執行早晨工作流：開啟 VS Code、Slack、Chrome 和 Terminal",
      "params": {
        "action": "run",
        "apps": "vscode,slack,chrome,terminal"
      }
    },
    {
      "query": "用 morning-profile.yaml 設定的工作流啟動今天的工作環境",
      "params": {
        "action": "run",
        "profile": "morning-profile.yaml"
      }
    },
    {
      "query": "新增 Notion 到晨間啟動程式清單",
      "params": {
        "action": "run",
        "mode": "add",
        "app": "notion"
      }
    }
  ],
  "params_schema": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "action": {
        "type": "string"
      },
      "app": {
        "type": "string"
      },
      "apps": {
        "type": "string"
      },
      "mode": {
        "type": "string"
      },
      "profile": {
        "type": "string"
      }
    },
    "required": [
      "action"
    ]
  },
  "license": "MIT",
  "status": "available",
  "source": "https://github.com/clibrary-hub/cli-tools/tree/main/manifests/G125-morning-boot"
}